<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Etymology">Etymology</h2><s=
pan class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span=
><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DPolynomial&amp;act=
