redirect" title=3D"Restriction of a function">restricted</a> to the reals, =
the resulting function is a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Real_f=
unction" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Real function">real function</a> th=
at maps reals to reals.
