itle=3D"Smooth function">smooth</a>, and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.or=
g/wiki/Entire_function" title=3D"Entire function">entire</a>.
</p><p><span class=3D"anchor" id=3D"evaluation"></span>The <a href=3D"https=
://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polynomial_evaluation" title=3D"Polynomial evaluat=
ion"><b>evaluation</b></a> of a polynomial is the computation of the corres=
